    <section class="install-section">
        <h2 class="install-title">快速安装</h2>
        <p>将 Token Tracker 集成到您的项目中，开始优化 token 使用。</p>

        <div class="install-steps">
            <div class="install-step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <h4>克隆仓库</h4>
                <p>git clone https://github.com/yourusername/token-tracker.git</p>
            </div>

            <div class="install-step">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <h4>安装依赖</h4>
                <p>cd token-tracker<br>npm install</p>
            </div>

            <div class="install-step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <h4>开始使用</h4>
                <p>node index.js record "任务名称" 输入token 输出token "优化措施"</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

